==English==

===Etymology===
{{suffix|en|food|ie}}. According to Wikipedia, the word was coined in 1984 by Paul Levy and Ann Barr for their book, ''The Official Foodie Handbook''.<!-- please replace Wikipedia with a reliable source --> However, Levy credits New York food critic Gael Greene with the coinage. The word was used by Greene in a 1980 article in New York Magazine.

